<beforebreak>(?U)\b([A-ZĆĆĆ][a-zĆ¶Ć¤Ć¼Ć]+nr|tel|[Gg]em|Pat|prov|Betr|lat|lfd|Lit|lt|Lz|Mask|mask|max|Mrd|mdal|me[dt]|phil|mhd|Mio?|mio|mind?|Mo|mod|nachm|nĆ¶rdlBr|neutr|Nhd|Nom|Nrn?|Num|Obj|od|dgl|offz)\.[\u00A0\s]{1,2}</beforebreak>
<afterbreak></afterbreak>
</rule>
<rule break="no">
